{"tid":1528703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太子恐襲傷者未有消息？尋晚走個時已經見月台有傷者cum緊保溫氈","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T23:26:02.000Z","uid":65210,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6c47b10971aa1b35d83ebd7351875e2c4da93c4b","tid":1528703,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"［一手］尋晚返屋企搭中屍速列車 太子班人累死咗一班手足？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1526339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1526339</a><br />\n<br />\n太子班傷者有消息未<br />\n尋日朋友搭中咗太子恐襲其中一班屍速列車<br />\n佢話臨走已經見到有一個傷者瞓咗係地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncum緊銀色個種保溫毯 有急救係隔離<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYWvfBy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYWvfBy.png&h=ddce558a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到有拎拐杖嘅老人家條頸有傷口見血<br />\n到依家都未有記者 媒體影到太子恐襲傷者嘅相？<br />\n除咗老豆搵仔話送咗去明愛 瑪嘉烈<br />\n就無其他消息？！！！<br />\n過咗24小時啦喎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下來自老豆搵仔1/9 11:41嘅Post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myL0COa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmyL0COa.jpg&h=261c5cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph67hOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph67hOb.jpg&h=40b1ec41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6UTXOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6UTXOb.jpg&h=1dbf82d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴晚太子站，至少10名傷者<br />\n6個紅色，2個黃色，2個綠色傷者<br />\n開頭警方報稱月台無傷者，拒絕救護車入站<br />\n3個紅色: 心口痛、頭部受傷、呼吸困難<br />\n2個黃色: 頭部受傷、呼吸困難<br />\n2個綠色: 膊頭甩骹，頭暈<br />\n其中7名傷者被警方要求經地鐵運去荔枝角地鐵站先送去明愛及瑪嘉烈"},{"pid":"b3bd96b8203f7c4d5490908d954cbedb4c254b47","tid":1528703,"uid":259345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"我忍左佢好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒 聽日麻包袋藍絲副校長 割唔割<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1b6b74eec6a4b36eaa3926202d75509d5448e68","tid":1528703,"uid":171192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"開頭警方報稱月台無傷者，拒絕救護車入站<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f4b8401b1d2cdbf89ea9e1188e5ecf0ae62246","tid":1528703,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"人道危機"},{"pid":"44b9f9dc7f062b8c19c2553f1efa62fad378e73d","tid":1528703,"uid":271280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:55:37.000Z","msg":"要咬住議員記者叫佢地咬住政府<br />\n已經係港版64"},{"pid":"d49a05d67fa9306e5078aed62fe0daafd676242c","tid":1528703,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1b6b74eec6a4b36eaa3926202d75509d5448e68","tid":1528703,"uid":171192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"開頭警方報稱月台無傷者，拒絕救護車入站<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"無記者影住 真係死得人⋯⋯"},{"pid":"a279ec1f9ecc98ffc8797f8c70623dbd13339b24","tid":1528703,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"石硤尾邨被打暈嘅細路仲未搵返<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.k